DOC.brief_summary: Primary objective:To investigate if BI 10773 affects the pharmacokinetics of ramipril and if ramipril affects the pharmacokinetics of BI 10773.
DOC.brief_title: Relative Bioavailability of Empagliflozin (BI 10773) and Ramipril Administered Together Compared to Empagliflozin (BI 10773) and Ramipril Alone in Healthy Volunteers
DOC.criteria: Inclusion criteria: 1. healthy male and female subjects Exclusion criteria: 1. Any relevant deviation from healthy conditions.
